## 1. List all atomic modeling claims made by the reference system model

### Reference Model Atomic Claims

#### Imports and Packages
1. The model defines a package `VehicleMassComplianceVerification`.
2. It imports `VerificationCases::*`.
3. It imports `Definitions::*`.
4. It defines a subpackage `Definitions`.
5. It defines a subpackage `Usages`.

#### Definitions Package
6. Defines a requirement `MassRequirement` with id '2'.
7. `MassRequirement` has attribute `massActual` of type `ISQ::mass`.
8. `MassRequirement` has attribute `massReqd` of type `ISQ::mass`.
9. `MassRequirement` has a constraint: `massActual <= massReqd`.
10. Defines a part `Vehicle`.
11. `Vehicle` has attribute `mass` of type `ISQ::mass`.
12. Defines a part `MassVerificationSystem`.
13. Defines a part `Scale`.
14. Defines a part `TestOperator`.
15. Defines an individual `TestVehicle1` of type `Vehicle`.
16. Defines an individual `TestVehicle2` of type `Vehicle`.
17. Defines an individual `TestSystem` of type `MassVerificationSystem`.
18. Defines a verification `MassTest`.
19. `MassTest` has an objective `massVerificationObjective`.
20. `massVerificationObjective` verifies requirement `massRequirement` of type `MassRequirement`.

#### Usages Package
21. Defines a requirement `vehicleMassRequirement` of type `MassRequirement` with id '2.1'.
22. `vehicleMassRequirement` has subject `vehicle` of type `Vehicle`.
23. `vehicleMassRequirement` maps `massActual = vehicle.mass`.
24. `vehicleMassRequirement` sets `massReqd = 2500 [SI::kg]`.
25. Defines a part `vehicle1_c2` of type `Vehicle`.
26. Defines a verification `vehicleMassTest` of type `MassTest`.
27. `vehicleMassTest` has subject `testVehicle` of type `Vehicle`.
28. `vehicleMassTest` has objective `vehicleMassVerificationObjective`.
29. `vehicleMassVerificationObjective` verifies `vehicleMassRequirement` via `massRequirement`.
30. `vehicleMassTest` defines action `collectData`.
31. `collectData` has input part `testVehicle` of type `Vehicle` from `vehicleMassTest.testVehicle`.
32. `collectData` has output `massMeasured` of type `ISQ::mass`.
33. `vehicleMassTest` defines action `processData`.
34. `processData` has input `massMeasured` of type `ISQ::mass` from `collectData.massMeasured`.
35. `processData` has output `massProcessed` of type `ISQ::mass`.
36. `vehicleMassTest` defines action `evaluateData`.
37. `evaluateData` has input `massProcessed` of type `ISQ::mass` from `processData.massProcessed`.
38. `evaluateData` has output `verdict` of type `VerdictKind` set by evaluating `vehicleMassRequirement` on `testVehicle(mass = massProcessed)`.
39. `vehicleMassTest` returns `verdict` of type `VerdictKind` from `evaluateData.verdict`.
40. Defines a part `massVerificationSystem` of type `MassVerificationSystem`.
41. `massVerificationSystem` performs `vehicleMassTest` with input part `testVehicle = vehicleUnderTest`.
42. `massVerificationSystem` has reference part `vehicleUnderTest` of type `Vehicle`.
43. `massVerificationSystem` has part `testOperator` of type `TestOperator`.
44. `massVerificationSystem` has part `scale` of type `Scale`.
45. `scale` performs `vehicleMassTest.collectData` with input part `testVehicle`.
46. `scale` measures `testVehicle.mass`.
47. `scale` outputs `massMeasured = measurement`.
48. Defines an individual `testSystem` of type `TestSystem` and `massVerificationSystem`.
49. `testSystem` has timeslice `test1` with reference individual `vehicleUnderTest` as `TestVehicle1` of type `vehicle1_c2` with `mass = 2500 [SI::kg]`.
50. `testSystem` then has timeslice `test2` with reference individual `vehicleUnderTest` as `TestVehicle2` of type `vehicle1_c2` with `mass = 2500 [SI::kg]`.
